== 正十邊形中的黃金比例 ==
無論是在給定的[[外接圓|外接圓]]<ref name="Henry Green">{{citation|title=Euclid's Plane Geometry, Books III–VI, Practically Applied, or Gradations in Euclid, Part II|first=Henry|last=Green|publisher=London: Simpkin, Marshall,& CO.|year=1861|page=116|isbn=|url=https://books.google.de/books?id{{=}}DjQDAAAAQAAJ&pg{{=}}PA116&dq{{=}}II.+Practically+decagon+Euklid+p.+116&hl{{=}}de&sa{{=}}X&ved{{=}}0ahUKEwj0oJXvr-7KAhVEYpoKHQ2OCW0Q6AEIHTAA#v{{=}}onepage&q{{=}}II.%20Practically%20decagon%20Euklid%20p.%20116&f{{=}}false|accessdate=2016-08-27|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305085544/https://books.google.de/books?id=DjQDAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA116&dq=II.+Practically+decagon+Euklid+p.+116&hl=de&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj0oJXvr-7KAhVEYpoKHQ2OCW0Q6AEIHTAA#v=onepage&q=II.%20Practically%20decagon%20Euklid%20p.%20116&f=false|dead-url=no}}. Retrieved 10 February 2016.</ref>或已知邊長要構造出正十邊形皆需要與[[黄金分割率|黃金比例]]相關的[[線段|線段]]才能作出。

*在給定的[[外接圓|外接圓]]構造正十邊形的過程中，其圓G的[[半徑|半徑]]{{Overline|GE<sub>3</sub>}}與線段{{Overline|AH}}的比為[[黃金比例|黃金比例]]
:<math>\frac{\overline{AM}}{\overline{MH}} = \frac{\overline{AH}}{\overline{AM}} = \frac{1+ \sqrt{5}}{2} = \Phi \approx 1.618</math>

* 在已知邊長構造正十邊形<ref name="Jürgen Köller">{{citation|title=Regelmäßiges Zehneck, → 3. Section "Formeln, Ist die Seite a gegeben ..."|first=Jürgen|last=Köller|publisher=|year=2005|url=http://www.mathematische-basteleien.de/zehneck.htm|accessdate=2016-08-27|archive-date=2016-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160831043258/http://www.mathematische-basteleien.de/zehneck.htm|dead-url=no}}. Retrieved 10 February 2016.</ref>的過程中，圓弧D半徑{{Overline|DA}}與線段{{Overline|E<sub>10</sub>F}}的比為黃金比例
:<math>\frac{\overline{E_1 E_{10}}}{\overline{E_1 F}} = \frac{\overline{E_{10} F}}{\overline{E_1 E_{10}}} = \frac{R}{a} = \frac{1+ \sqrt{5}}{2} =\Phi \approx 1.618 \text{.}</math>
